quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,67,"Waxaana yimid dadkii magaalada iyagoo ku bishaareysan (martida timid){2},"
  15,68,"(Luud) wuxuu yidhi: Kuwakanu waa martidaydii ee ha igu fadayxeynina."
  15,69,"Allena ka cabsada oo ha i ceebeynina."
  16,46,"Ama qabto iyagoo ku jira howlahooda, markaas ma ka baxsan karaan (Ciqaabka)?"
  16,47,"Ama qabto iyagoo ku sugan cabsi isa soo tarta. Rabbiggiinna waa Turid Badane, Naxariis Badan{2}."
  16,48,"Miyeyna u fiirsan wax kastoo uu Alle abuuray, (sida) hoosaskoodu ugu iishaan midig iyo bidix, oo ugu sujuudaan Alle iyagoo u khushuucsan."
  17,13,"Qof walbaana waxaan laasiminnay camalkiisa (loo qoray) luquntiisa, Waxaana u soo saari Maalinta Qiyaamaha Kitaab uu la kulmi isagoo fidsan{2}."
  17,14,"(Waxaa lagu odhan) Akhri Kitaabkaaga, adigaa isugu filan maanta xisaabiye ahaan."
  17,15,"Qofkii hanuuna, wuxuu u hunuunay naftiisa. Kii lumaana{2}, wuxuu uun u lumay naftiisa. Mana qaaddo nafi, denbi naf kale, oo ma cadaabno cidna jeer aan soo dirno Rasuul (u diga)."